But there are a few dark ones lurking behind the shining facade of her Kylie Cosmetics company. We’ll let you in on some of the issues that have plagued the Kardashian family and their various businesses. snippet.title: TESTING KYLIE COSMETICS | Lip Kits and Lip Gloss swatches | FIRST IMPRESSION!!!
snippet.description:
Testing Kylie cosmetics lip kits and lip glosses!!

Kylie Lip Kits - https://rstyle.me/+P3yk5WD0gY8TC1DMqWDaEQ
Kylie Lip Gloss - https://rstyle.me/+Mg13xvP40b5rSuamTMUGGQ

I tested out kylie cosmetics!! I ordered 8 Kylie lip kits, one liquid lipstick and 4 glosses and I swatched all of them on my lips. I've heard a lot about them being the same as colourpop which i do not agree with. I have also heard a lot of people say they are really drying which i didn't find at all, I actually really liked how they felt on the lips. I bought mine from Selfridges as i am in the UK. The lip kits are £26 and the glosses are £15 which i will link them all below. I tried to get a variety of shades as they are quite expenses but I personally don't think £26 for a lip liner and liquid lipstick is that bad.

snippet.title: Kylie Jenner Surprises Fan with Visit to Kylie Cosmetics Headquarters
snippet.description:
Ellen and Kylie Jenner teamed up to find deserving fans during premiere week and reward them with a total of $1 million, including Ashley Almonte, a huge fan of Kylie. Not only did Kylie give Ashley an exclusive tour of Kylie Cosmetics headquarters, she shocked her and her mom with $250,000, a portion of the proceeds from the Kylie Cosmetics Birthday Collection.

#KylieJenner
#KylieCosmetics
#TheEllenShow

snippet.title: KYLIE COSMETICS: THE VACATION COLLECTION | Review & Swatches
snippet.description:
HEY EVERYONE! Today I'm testing out the brand new KY|LIE COSMETICS 'Vacation Edition' Collection! This is Kylie's biggest launch to date and there are ALOT of products!!! I invited Nathan to join me and help swatch some of the highlighters because there were different kinds and I ran out of cheekbone room! I also create a look using the Take Me On Vacation eyeshadow palette, and swatch the matte liquid lipsticks + super glitter glosses! IS THE COLLECTION WORTH IT??? Watch and find out! XO

snippet.title: Kris Jenner - Introducing My Kris Jenner Collection
snippet.description:
Hi Dolls! 

Did you hear? I'm taking over!

There's truly nothing greater than a mother's love... except maybe this collection! Join me as I unbox and breakdown the full collab and talk all things Momager. 

My Kris Jenner Collection is available Mother's Day, May 13th,  2018 on http://kyliecosmetics.com.

Don't worry, Kylie will be back soon! 

xo Kris

snippet.title: KYLIE COSMETICS: KYLIGHTERS... Are They Jeffree Star Approved?!
snippet.description:
HEY EVERYONE!! OMG.... This video was so highly requested from you guys!! I just landed back from New York last night and HAD to film with these!! Today I'm testing out the much anticipated Kylie Cosmetics KYLIGHTERS! These are Kylie Jenner's version of a "highlighter" and I couldn't wait to see what this formula was like! I've heard so many mixed reviews since they launched... Had to see for myself what the hype was about! Are they Jeffree Star approved??? You might be surprised at the answer....
